---
title: Honey & Herb Haloumi Couscous Bowl with Roast Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Whip up a haloumi and couscous extravaganza in four easy steps. Drizzle over some honey to coat the haloumi and toss the couscous with some carrot and capsicum and it will look and taste like you’ve been cooking for hours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/653edb2db6b0d723385075f3-27d66340.jpeg
